➜17岁通过狗血政变当上皇后，洗白之战却输给一个八卦的妓女
http://www.sohu.com/a/432615279_624188	14966
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201118/95585be182e34f8cbc2241ac50b6a81b.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">如果有本小说里写到</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一位女子以<strong>嘴炮</strong>形式</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">孤身骂退十万大军</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你一定会觉得</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201118/bb36ef79ae1747eb8fa9d364fbcfe809.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但如果告诉你</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这件事是记录在</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">由<strong>北宋科学家、政治家沈括</strong>写的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">涉及<strong>古代中国科学、工艺技术及社会现象</strong>的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>《梦溪笔谈》</strong>里呢？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201118/bab38dcdf4be479cba6b92f495bbfc45.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
