<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center">首先</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">故事从这两个人讲起</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>李元昊</strong>——西夏开国皇帝</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>没藏黑云</strong>——西夏时期，野利家族大佬的女人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他们还有个孩子叫</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>李谅祚</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201118/91f61ae486e746fb854200b1d72925ac.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">故事的开头</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就是野利家族混太好了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">引起皇帝<strong>李元昊</strong>的注意</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">导致大佬被砍头</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而<strong>没藏黑云</strong>就被李元昊<strong>强占了</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">生下了<strong>李谅祚</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201118/b658f4d16f31489b916cd66936701ad8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">步入老年的李元昊</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不仅越来越多疑</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还越来越<strong>好色</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">先是把原配皇后给<strong>废了</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">然后把太子快过门的老婆<strong>抢了</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201118/6255a5e9ce394f2eb0132872c5e8a235.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">太子一看</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你这又废我妈又抢我媳妇</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">当爹也不能这么作吧</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">于是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在没藏黑云她哥的教唆下</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">太子准备把老爹李元昊给杀了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201118/950945afd2354ceeaa9b170ac2789327.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">行刺不太顺利</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">李元昊人没大事</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就是<strong>鼻子被削了</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而教唆杀人的没藏黑云她哥</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这时候主动跳出来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">迅速把太子和废后一块儿杀了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201118/4d54eadb9d0e4ef58c98fabc710ce5d0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">没想到的是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">刚杀了太子和废后没多久</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">李元昊也因伤势过重凉了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这下</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">西夏的政权跟<strong>白捡</strong>的一样</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">落入了没藏兄妹手里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而年仅一岁的私生子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">李谅祚</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就这么登上了皇位</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201118/77a26d7f847d4684976e5d9cfb9386f4.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">没藏黑云本就不是省油的灯</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">现在大权在握更是无法无天</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">天天<strong>约小鲜肉</strong>不带重样的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">结果八年后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">被气急败坏的<strong>某任前情夫</strong>杀了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只剩下她老哥把持着朝政</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201118/512f5d8f16584eaebca5570db46d3257.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这么些年</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">小皇帝李谅祚也长大了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有自个儿想法</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不乐意再当傀儡皇帝</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">开始和舅舅有了分歧</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">矛盾逐渐激化</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而最终点爆这个矛盾点的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就是我们<strong>真正的主角</strong>——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>梁氏</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201118/8e045adfbb57436bbdf027b10eaeeb1a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">梁氏是<strong>李谅祚他舅的儿媳妇</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">因为是汉人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以在西夏<strong>身份低微</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">凭这样的出生能混进没藏氏家门</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">已经算挺不错的了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">梁氏的梦想并不止于此</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201118/09cba78213fe4c8081769fde618fce88.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">早早就打着看小姑子的名号</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">经常进宫去混眼熟</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还不时出现在李谅祚左右</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">假装偶遇</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这一来二去两人还真看对了眼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有了私情</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201118/aeb06fdcb3804323845e87fa6e616331.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">如果私情被发现</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">第一个完蛋的就是梁氏</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">于是她决定<strong>先下手为强</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>告密</strong>说私情已经被发现</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">没藏氏那伙儿正商量暗杀他们</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">李谅祚听完寻思</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">等着被人宰不如先宰人算了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以借开私会的名义</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">召集没藏氏父子过来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">偷偷全杀了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201118/b1ddcfc5e5e64350a3bd59d12143720f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">然后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这一年</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">年仅17岁的梁氏</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就踩着丈夫全家的人头</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">成功拿下<strong>皇后宝座</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201118/31992fdcccd24539ae6b254076571742.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">梁氏当上皇后没几年</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">李谅祚就在一次和北宋的作战中</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">重伤嗝屁了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">24岁的梁氏</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就这么成了<strong>皇太后</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201118/37971876581e49f0a0d6482205642c7b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">新上位的皇帝才7岁</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">于是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">虽然才24但经历过大风大浪的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">皇太后梁氏</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就成了<strong>西夏背后真正的掌权大佬</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不仅周边亲戚都安排进宫干活</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">后期还把儿子给废了送出远门</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201118/d54fb494bc1f4cd199477257d46124e1.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">梁氏过得也不轻松</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">毕竟身为一个汉人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">她却当上了西夏皇太后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">加之李谅祚之前还推行汉化改革</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">更让人怀疑就是梁氏吹的枕边风</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这样的人当西夏大佬</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不免让人担心</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">会不会哪天一睡醒</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">西夏就已经成了北宋的地盘？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">为了消除疑惑洗白自己</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">梁氏不仅<strong>废除了李谅祚搞的汉化改革</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还决定——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201118/759207bf80f14f6dbb5e950bf706c7f4.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">于是以<strong>宋朝拒绝归还绥州</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">以及</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>禁止两国间私市</strong>作为借口</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">梁氏开启了西夏和宋朝</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">长达十年的战争</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201118/a84f9ac077da4ba5b612170fad07be91.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也就是在这些年的战争中</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">出现了我们开头的那一幕</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">梁氏派大军到北宋边境的<strong>顺宁寨</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">搞了波突袭</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这突发状况</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">把寨子里的人都整懵了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">准备是准备不了了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">支援赶也赶不及了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这下大家就跟羊圈里的羊一样</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">看着外面虎视眈眈的西夏大军</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201118/ac6041dd717a4630bd277f502c2aeab9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在此危急关头</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">城墙上出现了一个人影</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只见那人撩起裙摆</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">潇洒一甩</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">双手插在腰间</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">深吸了一口气</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">将全身的力量凝聚于丹田</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">然后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">开始了祖安式爆炸输出</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而她</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就是我们开篇的那位女人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>北宋的李氏</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201118/9486ece044c14e47bb6719a7d07cb5f8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<blockquote class="ql-align-center">
<strong>时寨兵至少，人心危惧。有倡姥李氏，得梁氏阴事甚详，乃掀衣登陴，抗声骂之，尽发其私。——《梦溪笔谈》</strong>
</blockquote>
<p class="ql-align-center">身为一名<strong>妓女</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">由于工作场合的特殊性</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">李氏就是身处吃瓜前沿的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>八卦大V</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就梁氏上位那点八卦</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">她早听过不知道多少次了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201118/9beb070189ef49f5bf2101deb8abac3f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">楼下这群西夏士兵</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就不一定听过了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就算听过</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也不敢在军营里乱说</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">毕竟私自谈论</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">要是传到太后耳朵里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">按梁氏的暴躁程度</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">整个营都给你一锅端了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201118/6488b10c494f405393987be5b6245a6b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">洞悉一切的李氏</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就站在城楼上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">大肆爆料梁氏八卦</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这下你是听也得听不听也得听</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不得不说这招真的是——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>笋爸爸给笋儿子开门</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>笋到家了</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">虽然西夏士兵们一直努力瞄准</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">企图当场射毙李氏</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201118/ee4736644b4e4893bef75943666c07da.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">西夏士兵虽然捂住了耳朵</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">却捂不住那颗<strong>八卦的心</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就这样怎么可能射得中人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而瞧见大家这副<strong>口嫌体正直</strong>的模样</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">李氏更兴奋了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不惜翻出老本</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>把别的不光彩的事儿也统统倒梁氏头上</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>更添油加醋说了一把</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201118/c9ae41bb39a14b21b34cbaa5d57d9cfd.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<blockquote class="ql-align-center">
<strong>虏人皆掩耳，并力射之，莫能中。——《梦溪笔谈》</strong>
</blockquote>
<p class="ql-align-center">这下西夏士兵<strong>真的慌了</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>这八卦听着一时爽</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>回家之后火葬场啊</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">要是被梁太后知道</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他们今儿搁这儿啥也没干</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">光听了<strong>《梁氏上位桃色版全集》</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">非把他们一个个扒皮抽筋不可</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">于是西夏士兵决定</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">先熘为上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201118/b999b98c49f14253abdbf693d8225315.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<blockquote class="ql-align-center">
<strong>李氏言愈丑，虏人度李终不可得，恐具得罪，遂托以他事，中夜解去。——《梦溪笔谈》</strong>
</blockquote>
<p class="ql-align-center">就这样</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这个北宋边境的小寨子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">愣是靠李氏的八卦爆料</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>给保住了</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201118/f25e7f2e909d4957a9681f14342fd1b9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">话说回战争</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">虽说西夏大部分时间都在挨揍</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但也有过像</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>永乐城之战</strong>的大胜利时刻</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不过</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这偶尔的高光时刻</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还是抵不过战争带来的负面影响</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>死伤惨重、经济下滑</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">都让<strong>西夏的内部矛盾越演越烈</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">梁氏的洗白剧演不下去</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不得已把儿子拉出来复位以平众怒</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201118/b496d18993524ff5b60cd66603828549.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">众怒未平<strong>人先凉</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">同年的十月</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">梁氏就为长达18年的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">西夏干政业务画上句号</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">曾经的小皇帝</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">终于能摆脱老妈的控制</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一切看起来似乎都有救了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201118/710ef8e99b9a420b866880b73a479401.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">其实一切都已经<strong>晚了</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">十几年的控制</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">早已成了小皇帝心中不可抹去的阴影</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">让他深陷自己又菜又可悲的泥潭</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">陷入了抑郁情绪难以自拔</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在老妈死后一年<strong>也跟着去了</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201118/305d8db5ff0a47e8a4086e5221f0ad00.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
